# Public build-time base URL used for absolute SEO / Open-Graph tags in index.html.
# Contains no secrets — safe to commit. Vite replaces %VITE_SITE_URL% at build time.
# Live domain since 2026-07-10: www.valanto.ch is the primary host (valanto.ch
# 308-redirects to it), managed in Vercel + Cloudflare DNS.
VITE_SITE_URL=https://www.valanto.ch
